## What does this mean?

{% raw %}    {{2}}{% endraw %}
LiaScript courses behave like **academic publications** rather than software projects:

{% raw %}    {{3}}{% endraw %}
| Model | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Wikipedia | Continuously updated |
| Open Source Software | Ongoing maintenance |
| Traditional Textbooks | Periodic major revisions |
| **LiaScript Courses** | **Create → Polish → Publish → Freeze** |

{% raw %}    {{4}}{% endraw %}
> This isn't necessarily bad! It aligns with the OER philosophy of "create once, share forever."

